message.body: Lindsey I'm sorry I neglected to wish you a happy day yesterday!! Hooray for you, I'm so glad you were born. Here's to you and to being grown ass women. Love you! ❤️❤️
Aww thanks Erin! 32 is the best year yet so far! I had my body scrubbed by elderly ladies with hard sponges!
Did you go to the Korean spa?? I love those ladies but I've never been scrubbed. Next time for sure. 32 is really good, you're going to love it!
I did go it was the greatest day.
